    "description": "Definition, Forms of Verbs (V1, V2, V3), Confusing Verbs and Special Adjective Forms.",
    "content": [
        {
            "type": "section",
            "title": "Introduction to Verb",
            "content": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "A **Verb** is a word used to describe an action, state, or occurrence. It is the most important part of a sentence.<br/>જે શબ્દ કોઈ ક્રિયા, સ્થિતિ કે હોવાપણું દર્શાવે છે તેને **ક્રિયાપદ (Verb)** કહે છે."
                },
                {
                    "type": "list",
                    "content": [
                        "**Action Verbs:** Run, Play, Eat, Write",
                        "**State Verbs:** Is, Am, Are, Was, Were, Have, Has"
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
